                                        3223
                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "BlenderBot (Roller et al., 2021): This is a largescale open- domain dialogue model pre- trained on the dialogue data scraped from social discussions on the web. BlenderBotmsc: This is the BlenderBot model finetuned on the MSC dataset. FID- RAG (Shuster et al., 2021): In this method, RAG- trained retriever (Lewis et al., 2020) is used to retrieve top- "
